    "This understanding of drivers' behavior empowers the system to respond to drivers' needs proactively.",
    "When integrated with other AI modules, like emotion detection [135], the Pose-Monitor AI-based Application contributes to a sweeping human behavior classification system.",
    "This integrated system can offer a more accurate and in-depth understanding of the driver's state, considerably improving the autonomous vehicle's interaction with its human occupants.The performance of the Pose-Monitor AI Applications in driver behavior analysis sets the stage for exploring cutting-edge machine learning and AI systems aiming to foster road safety.",
